.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113625\/sapa-vietnam-trekking-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113625\/sapa-vietnam-trekking-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113625\/sapa-vietnam-trekking-1080x810.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113625\/sapa-vietnam-trekking-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113625\/sapa-vietnam-trekking-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113625\/sapa-vietnam-trekking-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113625\/sapa-vietnam-trekking-163x122.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113625\/sapa-vietnam-trekking-240x180.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113625\/sapa-vietnam-trekking-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113625\/sapa-vietnam-trekking-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113625\/sapa-vietnam-trekking-1440x1080.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113625\/sapa-vietnam-trekking-30x23.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113625\/sapa-vietnam-trekking.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>It&#x2019;s super easy to arrange trekking in Sapa town because there are so many guides on the streets. The guides with the traditional clothes are the Hmong, a local tribe in the Sapa area. Some of these guides don&#x2019;t have a license to take tourists trekking. However, that doesn&#x2019;t necessarily mean that the trekking isn&#x2019;t good. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113404\/vietnam-local-573x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"239\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-35822 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 573px) 100vw, 573px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113404\/vietnam-local-573x810.jpg 573w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113404\/vietnam-local-300x424.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113404\/vietnam-local-600x848.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113404\/vietnam-local-424x600.jpg 424w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113404\/vietnam-local-239x338.jpg 239w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113404\/vietnam-local-1086x1536.jpg 1086w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113404\/vietnam-local-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113404\/vietnam-local-115x163.jpg 115w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113404\/vietnam-local-127x180.jpg 127w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113404\/vietnam-local-543x768.jpg 543w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\