n>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> If you can, it&#x2019;s best to arrange a reliable trekking itinerary through the hotel, guesthouse, or homestay. This way you can read reviews and have the most enjoyable, and informative, trekking experience possible.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"p1\">If you&#x2019;re looking for an easy package tour, you can book an all-in-one tour to Sapa, from Hanoi. This usually includes several other places too.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113409\/sapa-vietnam-adventure.jpg\" alt=\"sapa vietnam adventure\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sapa vietnam adventure\" class=\"wp-image-35821 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113409\/sapa-vietnam-adventure.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113409\/sapa-vietnam-adventure-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113409\/sapa-vietnam-adventure-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113409\/sapa-vietnam-adventure-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113409\/sapa-vietnam-adventure-1080x810.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113409\/sapa-vietnam-adventure-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113409\/sapa-vietnam-adventure-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113409\/sapa-vietnam-adventure-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113409\/sapa-vietnam-adventure-163x122.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113409\/sapa-vietnam-adventure-240x180.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113409\/sapa-vietnam-adventure-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113409\/sapa-vietnam-adventure-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113409\/sapa-vietnam-adventure-1440x1080.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113409\/sapa-vietnam-adventure-30x23.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113409\/sapa-vietnam-adventure.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"fansipan-mountain-and-cable-car\">Fansipan Mountain and Cable Car<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Soar through the clouds to the peak of Fansipan Mountain! This is the highest peak in Indochina and can be reached in just 15 minutes by cable car. Once at the top, there are fantastic views down to Sapa and the surrounding rice fields below. The cooler, wetter, climate of Sapa means that the peak can often be cloaked in a thick mist of clouds. However, this is still a beautiful experience! Enjoy looking down onto clouds below, and at the giant Buddha looming above.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/206&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113600\/guide-sapa-vietnam.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113600\/guide-sapa-vietnam-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113600\/guide-sapa-vietnam-342x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Trekking in Sapa: Balancing on the Borders of the Ricefields\" height=\"600\" width=\"342\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The cable car station is located in Sapa town, about a 30-minute walk from Notre Dame. Try to go as early as possible to beat the crowds. Note that once you arrive at the top cable car station, it&#x2019;s another 30-minute walk to the top.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>It&#x2019;s open from 7.30 am-5.30 pm. Tickets cost VND 700,000 for adults.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Before the arrival of the cable car, you could only reach the mountain by hiking. This is still an option for those that have good fitness, as it&#x2019;s an intermediate hike. It can be done in a 2-day trek or a 1-day trek, returning by cable car.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113553\/accommodation-sapa-vietnam-615x810.jpg\" alt=\"accommodation sapa vietnam\"><\/noscript><img width=\"256\" height=\"338\" alt=\"accommodation sapa vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-35417 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 615px) 100vw, 615px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113553\/accommodation-sapa-vietnam-615x810.jpg 615w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113553\/accommodation-sapa-vietnam-300x395.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113553\/accommodation-sapa-vietnam-600x791.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113553\/accommodation-sapa-vietnam-455x600.jpg 455w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113553\/accommodation-sapa-vietnam-256x338.jpg 256w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/