k-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"sapa-lake\">Sapa Lake&#xA0;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The heart of the town is the beautiful lake that sits in the middle, surrounded by stunning mountains. Approaching Sapa and seeing a view of the town reflected in the crystal clear water is absolutely breathtaking. Wander along the outskirts of the lake and take in the fresh Sapa air. Walk here at night, and make a stop for some food or drink in one of the lakeside cafes.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113400\/sapa-market.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-35831 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113400\/sapa-market.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113400\/sapa-market-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113400\/sapa-market-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113400\/sapa-market-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113400\/sapa-market-1080x810.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113400\/sapa-market-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113400\/sapa-market-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113400\/sapa-market-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113400\/sapa-market-163x122.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113400\/sapa-market-240x180.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113400\/sapa-market-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113400\/sapa-market-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113400\/sapa-market-1440x1080.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113400\/sapa-market-30x23.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113400\/sapa-market.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"sapa-market\">Sapa Market<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Close to the lake is the renowned sapa market. This is the main market in the area, although there are several others. Here you can find typical handicrafts of the local Hmong Tribe, in the traditional colors. Not only this, but you can buy spices, fresh fruit, and vegetables. This is an excellent way to see local life in action and pick up a few souvenirs from your trip.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:&#xA0;<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/thailand\/best-market-bangkok\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The best night market in Bangkok<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"besttime\"><strong>Best Time to Travel to Sapa<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Visit Sapa from March to May and September to November for the best temperatures. To be sure of stunning green rice fields, visit between May and September. Be aware that it does rain a lot more during these months. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113610\/homestay-vietnam-sapa-573x810.jpg\" alt=\"homestay vietnam sapa\"><\/noscript><img width=\"239\" height=\"338\" alt=\"homestay vietnam sapa\" class=\"wp-image-35399 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 573px) 100vw, 573px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113610\/homestay-vietnam-sapa-573x810.jpg 573w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113610\/homestay-vietnam-sapa-300x424.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113610\/homestay-vietnam-sapa-600x848.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113610\/homestay-vietnam-sapa-424x600.jpg 424w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113610\/homestay-vietnam-sapa-239x338.jpg 239w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113610\/homestay-vietnam-sapa-1086x1536.jpg 1086w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113610\/homestay-vietnam-sapa-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113610\/homestay-vietnam-sapa-115x163.jpg 115w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016