ck-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"transport\"><strong>How to Get from Hanoi to Sapa?<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>From Hanoi, the buzzing capital of Vietnam, there are several options to get to Sapa. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transport-hanoi-sapa\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Get your bus or train tickets here.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Here are 6 guesthouses and <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/vietnam\/hotels-sapa\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hotels in Sapa<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115822\/guide-hanoi-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"guide hanoi vietnam flag\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"guide hanoi vietnam flag\" class=\"wp-image-31522 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115822\/guide-hanoi-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115822\/guide-hanoi-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115822\/guide-hanoi-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115822\/guide-hanoi-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/