nterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115857\/hanoi-vietnam-1060x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"the-train-from-hanoi-to-sapa\"><strong>The Train from Hanoi to Sapa<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The sleeper train will bring you to Lao Cai, 40 kilometers from the Chinese border. The journey takes about 8 hours and the price of a ticket starts at 20 USD onwards.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115802\/best-things-to-do-hanoi-train-street.jpg\" alt=\"best things to do hanoi train street\"><\/noscript><img width=\"448\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best things to do hanoi train street\" class=\"wp-image-31528 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115802\/best-things-to-do-hanoi-train-street.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115802\/best-things-to-do-hanoi-train-street-300x226.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115802\/best-things-to-do-hanoi-train-street-600x453.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115802\/best-things-to-do-hanoi-train-street-795x600.jpg 795w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115802\/best-things-to-do-hanoi-train-street-1073x810.jpg 1073w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115802\/best-things-to-do-hanoi-train-street-448x338.jpg 448w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115802\/best-things-to-do-hanoi-train-street-1536x1159.jpg 1536w, 