:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transport-hanoi-sapa\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Get your bus or train tickets here.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/sapa-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Check out all hotels and homestays in Sapa under $50<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113603\/Ricefields-sapa.jpg\" alt=\"Ricefields sapa\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Ricefields sapa\" class=\"wp-image-35401 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113603\/Ricefields-sapa.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113603\/Ricefields-sapa-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113603\/Ricefields-sapa-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113603\/Ricefields-sapa-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113603\/Ricefields-sapa-1080x810.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113603\/Ricefields-sapa-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/23113603\/Ricefields-sapa-1536x1152.jpg 